![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/c209521e-2abc-4dff-a5bc-9e529888b3e2/284.jpg)

5 years ago, Sony Animation released a film that changed how we viewed Spider-Man forever when Spider-Man: Into The Spider-Verse was released in theaters around the globe. Half a decade later, and its highly anticipated sequel Spider-Man: Across The Spider-Verse hopes to do the same thing. Does it succeed in that mission? Is it better than its predecessor? Is this the rare stellar superhero sequel or is it another Wonder Woman 84 situation? Tune in and find out!

If you can, please leave us a **_review_** on [**ITunes**](https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/major-issues-podcast/id1321720972) so we can grow our audience and grow as podcasters! Rate us where ever podcasts are found. Don't forget to check out our merchandise! All episodes of Major Issues are brought to you by **ComicBook Clique**, the only stop for the latest and greatest things to come to comic books and comic book media.

